attributes.description:
[Tech Preview] Dashboard to display chargeback information based on the Elasticsearch Service Billing and the Elasticsearch integrations.

This provides a breakdown of ECU per deployment, per data stream, per day.

Please note: breakdown per Tier is not supported (yet).

# Version 0.1.0
